Sphere² Lamp BLE Remote Android App Privacy Policy
--------------------------------------------------

In order to discover and connect to the Sphere² Lamp, the app searches nearby bluetooth low energy (BLE) devices and displays a list of the available devices (name and hardware address).
It does not store, collect, upload or share this data. Neither does it use the found devices for any kind of location determination.

Your data is not collected, used, transferred, shared or otherwise utilized.

